| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7111 — Recovery Inhibition (flocker)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: c85d8f29-fc73-5e6e-8b05-454eefcc6f0a"
